title: S3 EP7: Talk Derby to Me with Tim Meltreger
description:
This week, Maggie & Tim are joined by the Psychonic writer Tim Meltreger to talk Derby with them! The gang discusses Season Three Episode Seven, the one where Juliet goes undercover as part of a badass roller derby team and we all ship "Shules" even harder than usual!
